import { Box, Button, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'


const TodoAdder = () => {
  return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Box>
                <TextField
                    style={{width:400}}
                    id="standard-textarea"
                    label="add todo"
                    placeholder="text..."
                    multiline
                    variant="standard"
                    onChange={handle}
                />
                <Button style={{height:45}} variant="contained">Outlined</Button>
            </Box>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default TodoAdder
